data.name: Blue Cheese Dressing
data.quickTastyDescription: A rich and tangy dressing perfect for salads or dipping!
detailedCookingInstructions: In a bowl, combine the crumbled blue cheese, mayonnaise, sour cream, and white vinegar.
Mix well until the ingredients are combined and the blue cheese is broken down into smaller pieces.
Add milk to reach your desired consistency. Mix until smooth.
Season with garlic powder, salt, and black pepper to taste. Adjust seasoning as necessary.
Serve immediately or refrigerate for up to a week.
